      ### Package-Specific Troubleshooting

      ```mermaid
      flowchart TD
        A[Package Issue] --> B{Which Package Type?}
        B -->|eslint-config| C[Check ESLint Configuration]
        B -->|prettier-config| D[Check Prettier Configuration]
